        <p begin="00:03:51.880" end="00:03:55.540" tts:direction="ltr">you'll see that it will be added here in
<br />the data source.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:55.540" end="00:03:58.520" tts:direction="ltr">If I select ARB and B, for instance,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:58.520" end="00:04:00.760" tts:direction="ltr">you'll see that I'm now</p>
        <p begin="00:04:00.760" end="00:04:03.800" tts:direction="ltr">seeing the dimensions and measures in that
